Package com.github.stasgora.observetree

Class SettableProperty<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.stasgora.observetree.Observable
      • com.github.stasgora.observetree.SettableProperty<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of the actual observable data type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SettableObservable
    public class SettableProperty<T>
extends Observable
implements java.io.Serializable
    A wrapper class that encapsulates another object - modelValue - and notifies it's listeners when the modelValue is set. It supports defaultValue for the modelValue that can be set and reset to.
    Author:
    Stanisław Góra
    See Also:
    SettableObservable, Serialized Form
